OL,3,CMore than 60 firefighters at scene of
OL,4,Clarge fire on industrial estate
OL,6,FA large fire has broken out at an
OL,7,Findustrial unit in Oldbury.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Fblaze on the Rood End Road Industrial
OL,11,FEstate shortly before 5:30am today.
OL,13,FWest midlands Fire Service said the
OL,14,Fincident involves a single storey
OL,15,Ffactory building.
OL,17,FThere are more than 60 firefighters on
OL,18,Fthe scene, using 10 fire engines and
OL,19,Fspecialist equipment including
OL,20,Fhydraulic platforms..
